Sumo is an application for the ATmega328P microcontroller.

It manages a 2 line 16 character LCD display via an 8-bit parallel interface.
It is connected to the other mpus via the TWI.

To build and install the application :-

  $ make
  $ cd ../bali
  $ avril sumo

To build and install the application and bootloader :-

  connect the ICSP cable between bali and sumo

  $ make image
  $ cd ../bali
  $ (. ./defs.sh && cd ../sumo && make avp)

